Package: lwgeom
Version: 0.0-0
Title: Liblwgeom Bindings for Simple Features 
Description: Access to some of the functions found in liblwgeom, the geometry library used by PostGIS. Those that are directly exposed by the C interface of GEOS are to be found in package sf.
